snippet.title: Female Empowerment Frag Comm Collaboration
snippet.description:
This video is a celebration of the fabulous females of the fragrance world, past and present.

A huge thank you to all my contributors!!

Time Stamps and links below:
1:22 Andreas - Servus Vibes Born This Way cover
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCHiJsw0OuDej0p7IesPlmhw/videosSinging us in with 
6:23 Liz Moores from Papillon Perfumery Salome https://papillonperfumery.co.uk/
8:22 Holly Golightley - Givenchy Immortelle Tribal - https://www.youtube.com/c/MissHollyGolightley/videos
9:28 Madeleine - Vegan Perfume Girl - Floral Street Iris Goddess https://instagram.com/veganperfumegirl?utm_medium=copy_link
10:21 Sarah Maccartney 4160 Tuesdays - Angela Flanders Lawn - https://www.4160tuesdays.com/
11:41 Karine Olfactive Stories - Chanel 1932
https://www.youtube.com/c/OlfactiveStories/videos
12:50 Brendan Rodriguez - Brendan.MagicTV
https://www.youtube.com/c/MagicianBrendanRodrigues
14:28 Moody Boo - Rose All Dae Gallagher Perfumes
https://www.youtube.com/c/MOODYBOOREVIEWSfubar1963/videos
15:40 Brooke Belldon - Hooha - Germaine Cellier Fracas Robert Piguet
https://hoohaa.co.uk/pages/subscription
18:04 Joss Jane - Maison Lancome Oud Ambroisie, Narciso Rodriguez Musc Noir
https://www.youtube.com/c/JossJane/videos
19:42 Lily, Evie and Chris  Frag-mental Tom Ford Noir De Noir and Black Orchid Parfum
https://www.youtube.com/c/FRAGMENTAL/videos
21:36 Eva The Fragrance Test Tube - Fragrant Females throughout history - Issara Dusita
https://www.youtube.com/c/FragranceTestTube/videos
23:14 Gabbi The Fragrantician - Salme Papillon Perfumery
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgD6-kgqv9EC9sRsrVq3gww/videos
24:15 Amanda Italy Vintage Perfume
https://www.youtube.com/c/ItalyvintageperfumeLonghurst/videos
25:24 Erin Sullivan Fragrance- La Douceur De Siam Dusita Parfums
https://www.youtube.com/c/ErinSullivanFragranceBeauty/videos
26:26 Giveaway info - Smoulder and Bernadette Margaret Evelyn Theresa
27:26 Freddie Albrighton Bernadette Margaret Evelyn Theresa
https://www.freddiealbrighton.com/
30:23 Penelope Treat - Beautiful Magnolia Estée Lauder https://instagram.com/penelopeanntreat?utm_medium=copy_link
31:47 Tara Olfactofiles - Maya Njie Nordic Cedar 
https://www.youtube.com/c/Olfactofiles/videos
33:07 Shanna  - De Parfum Lade - Yvresse Yves Saint Laurent https://instagram.com/deparfumlade?utm_medium=copy_link
33:54 Scentualise Senior courtesy of Bazza at Scentualise - and Fragrances Frank
https://www.youtube.com/c/Scentualise/videos
36:14 Frances - Happiness Sparkles - CK Eternity
https://www.youtube.com/user/frances181253/videos
37:46 Erin Sullivan Fragrance sings us out with Six Heart of Stone - a huge thank you and massive hugs to Erin for submitting such a beautiful song whilst dealing with your own heart break. 
https://www.youtube.com/c/ErinSullivanFragranceBeauty/videos
42:56 Final words - Womens Aid https://www.womensaid.org.uk/

For the giveaway comments must be in the comments section of the video, live chat comments wont be counted.  Winner needs a UK address for prize to be sent to.  I"m sorry that this can't be international but UK postage rules do not permit me to post abroad, why not participate and nominate a UK based friend for the prize if you're a winner?
